But in reply to faxafoli. What I found that I did wrong with the initial install was to add to the scenery in the wrong order, priority 1 and 2. 
I.e FSX\aerosoft\Iceeland X\Iceland X - priority 1 & 2 Folders. Folder 1 has highest priority then hey presto you get your autogen scenery of Reykjavik. Hope that this is of some help and guidance? Nice to meet you all
